NLTK - Natural language tool kit - python

NLP - Natural language processing -  process to getting a computer to understand the natural language


# installation

 - pip install nltk

 terminologies -

 1. Tokenizing -
    > word tokenizerss - this separated by words
    > sentence tokenizers - this separates by sentence

 2.corparas -
    >the corpara is just a budy of text

 3.Lexicons -
    > words and their meanings

- Stop Words
(a,the,an ) - those kind of word which you really don't care about.

- Stemming
stem of reading is 'read' - main stem of a word

-speach tagging
